WEBVTT

00:02:56.248 --> 00:03:00.898
Now Ariel spends the play hoping to repay
his debt and earn his freedom,

00:03:00.898 --> 00:03:04.818
while Caliban is enslaved indefinitely,
or at least as long

00:03:04.818 --> 00:03:07.458
as Prospero is in charge.

00:03:07.458 --> 00:03:09.558
For these reasons and many more,


00:03:09.558 --> 00:03:13.538
